Definition: bushy plant of Old World salt marshes and sea beaches having prickly leaves
Example: burned to produce a crude soda ash
Synonyms: barilla, glasswort, kali, kelpwort, Salsola_kali, Salsola_soda, shrub, bushy, plant, of, Old, World, salt, marshes, and, sea, beaches, having, prickly, leaves, burned, to, produce, a, crude, soda, ash
Category: noun.plant
